ComicInfo.Series: Grimm Fairy Tales presents Tales From Oz
ComicInfo.Summary:
Zenescope's first Oz series quickly became one of the top-selling comic book titles on shelves in 2013 and 2014. By re-inventing the classic tale in an intense and daring fantasy series, readers fell in love with the infamous Oz characters all over again. Now this new installment of Zenescope's new Oz mythos follows the mesmerizing, and many times frightening, origins of the Witches of OZ as their backstories will be told! The realm of Oz has many dark secrets and now those secrets will be revealed!
